information: PANINKRET Chem.-Pharm. Vertriebsges. mbH is a national and international company selling animal and plant extracts from well-known production partners. The production partner for animal extracts is Paninkret Chem.-Pharm. Werk GmbH. Our plant extracts and fresh plant pressed juice powders predominantly originate from Salus Haus Nachf. GmbH & Co KG and Walther Schoenenberger Pflanzensaftwerk GmbH. Our partners are leading companies in their sectors. Together, we place the highest value on the quality of the products sold by us, which are mainly manufactured in Germany. To emphasise this claim even more, since 2001 we have used a management system in accordance with DIN EN ISO 9001: 2015. On request, a number of our products can be Koscher certified via the OK Kosher Certification and can also be offered in organic quality in accordance with DE-ÖKO-003. Since 2014, we have held a permit to trade in substances in accordance with Section 67 AMG (German Medicinal Products Act). We look forward to hearing from you!
